trans-unit.source: Retrieves a list of individual key versions in the Key Vault as JSON Web Key structures that contain the public part of a stored key.
trans-unit.target: Retrieves a list of individual key versions in the Key Vault as JSON Web Key structures that contain the public part of a stored key.

trans-unit.source: The LIST VERSIONS operation is applicable for all versions having the same key name.
trans-unit.target: The LIST VERSIONS operation is applicable for all versions having the same key name.

trans-unit.source: The full key identifier, attributes, and tags are provided in the response.
trans-unit.target: The full key identifier, attributes, and tags are provided in the response.

trans-unit.source: You may use the nextLink field via an HTTP GET to retrieve the next set of results, which will include another nextLink field.
trans-unit.target: You may use the nextLink field via an HTTP GET to retrieve the next set of results, which will include another nextLink field.

trans-unit.source: The enumeration is completed if and only if nextLink is empty.
trans-unit.target: The enumeration is completed if and only if nextLink is empty.

trans-unit.source: Authorization: Requires the keys/list permission.
trans-unit.target: Authorization: Requires the keys/list permission.
